                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10285" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1542</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">248 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">凯利泰之殇：战略投资者与创始人的权力博弈</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Downfall of Kinetic: Power Struggles between Strategic Investors and Founders</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李红玉，陆智强，彭镇（通讯作者）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海凯利泰医疗科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股权结构；公司治理；回购条款；控制权争夺；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Equity Structure; Corporate Governance; Repurchase Clause; Control Contest</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上市公司凯利泰医疗科技有限公司（以下简称“凯利泰”）的董事长状告自家上市公司，引起资本市场一片哗然。本教学案例将聚焦于这一事件，首先介绍了凯利泰的发展历程与股权结构，以及凯利泰创始人团队与战略投资者涌金投资控股有限公司（以下简称“涌金投资”）的关系。其次，介绍了此次冲突的关键事件，即凯利泰投资关联企业利格泰股份有限公司（以下简称“利格泰”），并签署股权回购条款；然后，介绍利格泰触发回购条款，凯利泰创始人团队和涌金投资因回购争议所引发的控制权博弈，引导学员学习资本结构、股东权益、公司治理理论等相关知识点。具体目标包括：让学员理解股权结构与公司治理之间的关系；让学员掌握关联交易的风险及治理方法；引导学员思考如何保护投资者的利益，树立正确的经营与投资价值观。通过案例学习和讨论训练，希望能够培养和强化学员的思维与分析能力，并实现课程思政目的。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The chairman of Kinetic Medical Technology Co., Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as “Kinetic”) filed a lawsuit against his own listed company, causing a sensation in the capital market. This teaching case focuses on this incident, first outlining Kinetic’s development trajectory, equity structure, and the relationship between its founding team and strategic investor Yongjin Investment Holdings Co., Ltd. (“Yongjin Investment”). It then introduces the key trigger of the conflict: Kinetic’s investment in an affiliated enterprise, Ligatech Co., Ltd. (“Ligatech”), and the signing of a “performance compensation” (earn-out) agreement. Subsequently, it discusses how the triggering of a repurchase clause led to a power struggle regarding repurchase obligations between Kinetic’s founding team and Yongjin Investment, guiding learners to understand concepts such as capital structure, shareholder rights, and corporate governance. The intended learning outcomes include: enabling students to comprehend the relationship between equity structure and corporate governance, mastering the risks and governance methods of related-party transactions, and prompting critical thinking on how to protect investor interests and establish sound operational and investment values. Through case discussion and analysis, the goal is to cultivate and enhance learners’ thinking and analytical abilities, as well as fulfill the ideological and political objectives of the course.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">委托代理理论；投资者利益保护</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
